net.derquinse.common.io
Class MemoryByteSource

java.lang.Object
  com.google.common.io.ByteSource
      net.derquinse.common.io.MemoryByteSource

@Beta
public abstract class MemoryByteSource
extends ByteSource

Base class for byte sources that are guaranteed to be stored in memory, either heap or direct buffers. The byte source may be contiguous or backed a list of chunks. Total size must fit in an integer. The default chunk size is 8 KB.

Author:
Andres Rodriguez
